# Build context for the I5 image is this `Intermediate/` directory, but the image
# only needs the dockerize-service entry point + the shared currency-core package.
# Ignore everything by default, then re-include just those two trees and strip cruft.

*

!dockerize-service
!shared

# Strip heavy / irrelevant files from the re-included trees.
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/node_modules
**/tests
**/.DS_Store
# NOTE: README.md files are intentionally kept — currency-core's pyproject.toml
# declares `readme = "README.md"`, so setuptools needs it during pip install.
